{"tid":2305271,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"準備反攻大陸？國民黨高唱「復我河山救我同胞」","createTime":"2020-11-29T13:21:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-29T13:43:29.000Z","uid":337052,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4f2521e05f8a348834783bb8836c3dcff5be02bf","tid":2305271,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T13:21:04.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">國民黨黃復興慶黨慶 江啟臣帶頭高唱「復我河山救我同胞」</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n2020/11/29 20:59<br />\n〔記者蔡文居／台南報導〕今年為國民黨建黨126周年，國民黨黃復興黨部慶祝黨慶，今晚在台南市北區光武里活動中心舉辦「復興啟程」聯歡會，<span class=\"red\">國民黨黨主席江啟臣南下出席，除頒獎表揚3位百歲人瑞黨員外，也帶領黨員齊唱國語老歌「國恩家慶」，大家一起揮舞國旗高唱「齊奮起齊奮起 復我河山 救我同胞」，現場氣氛高昂。</span><br />\n<br />\n江啟臣於晚上7點多抵達會場，受到與會近200位黨員的熱烈歡迎，包括國民黨台南市議員謝龍介、王家貞、洪玉鳳、許至椿、李中岑、李鎮國、前立委高思博、南市黨部主委莊占魁等人也出席，並一起高唱老歌「國恩家慶」、「藍天白雲」，最後江啟臣還被要求自唱一首「月亮代表我的心」，為現場炒熱氣氛。<br />\n<br />\n江啟臣致詞表示，國民黨一路走來，我們的DNA就是韌性和創新，也因為孫中山總理的理念跟思想，讓我們經過了百年仍然可以凝聚人心，即便我們遭遇到困難跟挑戰，尤其在民主政治的競爭當中，選舉絕對有贏有輸，不管中央跟地方都是如此，但是作為一個政黨，我們不能因為一次、兩次選舉的失敗就放棄，就不堅持我們的理念和想法，只要我們繼續堅持，和人民站在一起，以民為本，最後人民一定還是會給我們機會，認同我們。<br />\n<br />\n他說，國民黨作為目前最大的在野黨，責任也相對重大，因為人民對我們有期待，特別是面對一個蠻橫、霸道、無良的執政黨的時候，大家絕對把目光放在在野黨，所以這是我們該為人民爭取權益，捍衛權益的時候，也感謝所有黨員先進對黨的支持與不離不棄。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/3366164\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F3366164&d=73P4J9mxZbud55ZbF8SGibvH1KbbL%2ByyGPsbuV3zdoQ%3D&h=77119307\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F3366164&h=15fa3791\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/3366164</a>"},{"pid":"34fc833dee7e46d48ce2bec7d387c1de1a120373","tid":2305271,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T13:23:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WXm7PfN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWXm7PfN.png&h=24baa447&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n恭喜周庭和黃之峰<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2296813\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2296813</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c9a1a09281cff6cc72806c6bb323d176ea3d90c8","tid":2305271,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T13:24:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2vGTavG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2vGTavG.png&h=6ad271ba&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e8ebf42d22c83735575babeab752c10c4ee25161","tid":2305271,"uid":237562,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T13:24:17.000Z","msg":"台灣大中華膠"},{"pid":"a4edec4e521134107184c3faaa52c44e0263d979","tid":2305271,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T13:26:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fKeNJHa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfKeNJHa.png&h=c224e9f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/itJCmuz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FitJCmuz.png&h=46a67ec0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gV0k3KV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgV0k3KV.png&h=43ca085b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qQte8ce.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqQte8ce.png&h=0b515182&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U0JFZdR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU0JFZdR.png&h=d0e14ab6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f33deecd7e3068f4bf667fea498865547f8f92b5","tid":2305271,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e8ebf42d22c83735575babeab752c10c4ee25161","tid":2305271,"uid":237562,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T13:24:17.000Z","msg":"台灣大中華膠"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T13:36:59.000Z","msg":"台灣的藍屍"},{"pid":"6c06fd7e365631fb02b670ca1200c3f2de11f80a","t